nodes.text: The garbage proccessing facility was a facility for processing garbage at Kamino Station X on the planet Kamino; in 1 BBY the Rebel Alliance discovered a document made by the Lead Cloning Technician in the garbage processing facility.
The garbage processing facility was mentioned in the Dark Apprentice Databank entry in the PS3 and Xbox 360 versions of the 2010 video game Star Wars: The Force Unleashed II.
